{"tid":2240863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] [重開] 2020川普總統競選歌曲，中文版上線啦！","createTime":"2020-10-13T03:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T19:52:45.000Z","uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4109087931abb003812fae607044d3d4ff7b75","tid":2240863,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gs1C0u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gs1C0u.png&h=71ea6e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n選舉人票 我想要帶你回家<br />\n在那深夜民調 哪管它是真是假<br />\n請你盡情搖擺 佛州賓州北卡<br />\n2020 Vote Trump 你知道嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我是最好的總統 拜登最壞候選人<br />\n前面什麼雞掰眾議院<br />\n我拿腳往裡踹<br />\n如此動感的裴洛西 非得擱在門口彈劾<br />\n<br />\n我蹦迪的民調上面怎麼能有落後<br />\n賓州落 後7趴 <br />\n全國落後12趴<br />\n通俄逃稅性騷擾<br />\nCNN瞅我也懵<br />\n不管多病都不能離開橢圓辦公室<br />\n確診武肺 必須跟我整齊劃一<br />\n<br />\n來左邊跟我一起叫川普<br />\n在你右邊兒叫一聲凍蒜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來左邊跟我一起喊川普<br />\n在你右邊兒再喊凍蒜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在你胸口上比劃一個Joe Biden<br />\n左邊兒右邊兒搖搖頭<br />\n辯論表現就像一個失智咖<br />\n跪拜閃耀的中國<br />\n<br />\n選舉人票 我想要帶你回家<br />\n在那深夜民調 哪管它是真是假<br />\n請你盡情搖擺 密州俄州緬因<br />\nMAGA Vote Trump 你知道嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce63d71c04849f6f5cdfc0e2df80c8d3bac5732","tid":2240863,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"呢段侵侵宣傳MV好有青春活力<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173026\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2173026</a>"},{"pid":"452d41ee462e317678ece75684b6edad639de1f4","tid":2240863,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ce63d71c04849f6f5cdfc0e2df80c8d3bac5732","tid":2240863,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"呢段侵侵宣傳MV好有青春活力<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173026\" target=\"_blank\">h